headline: These Stocks Moved the Most Today: Super Micro, Tesla, U.S. Steel, Palantir, AT&T, Meta Platforms, Apple, and More

headline: Honeywell lowers sales guidance on Bombardier deal
summary: Honeywell (HON) stock is in focus as the company cuts its full-year sales outlook after signing an agreement with Bombardier with an estimated lifetime value of $17 billion. Julie Hyman and Josh Lipton outline what investors need to know. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination here. This post was written by Naomi Buchanan.
